target.message:
Interpret loading from saved data of blank stylesheet as implying the
default should be used. However, append '\n' to an actual blank stylesheet,
so that upon saving and loading, it can be recognised as an intentionally blank
one. This is for backward compatibility with the fact that an empty string
used to be what was stored when no changes to the default stylesheet had
been made.
added a few more messages to the outbox

Quick fix for phasematrix buffered mode, forcing output to be on every experiment
Should be reverted once labscript implementation of StaticDigitalOutput for phasematrix is fixed (needs pseudoclock parent faked)

Merged in monashspinor/blacs/run_repeat (pull request #25)

Add a 'run repeat' attribute to shot files.

Approved-by: Jan Werkmann <jan.wrk.fb@gmail.com>
Remove vertical line in tab frame header

Added basic support for Image output types (for the SLM).

device_base_class has not been extended to support remote_value_checking for this output type
font_panel_settings has not been extended to support saving and loading of the front panel for these output types.

That said, I've added enough code to these classes so that blacs doesn't break when you have a device with Image outputs.

Requires labscript_utils changeset: 74e3a9328055
All changes made so far are backwards compatible with existing labscript_devices.

Remove timeout on polling second queue during experiment. Now, during an
experiment the loop will block for 0.5 seconds at a time waiting for the end
of the experiment, and then each loop it will also check without blocking if
there was an abort or restart.
